quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  18,45,Cite for them vzor this zivot mat rad zavlazit lenze my send sky produce zasadit zem potom they turn into hay blown zranit GOD bol able do ROBIT all things
  18,46,Peniaze dieta bol radost this zivot righteous robota zadovazit eternal recompense z tvoj Lord daleko lepsi hope
  18,47,Dni pod when my wipe mountains ona see zem barren My zvolat them all nie vlavo single 1 z them
  18,48,They presented tvoj Lord rad. Ona pojdem us individuum iba mat rad my created ona initially. Indeed this bol co ona reklamacia will never happen
  18,49,Rekord shown ona see guilty fearful z its contents They say Woe do us. Ako pod this rezervovat si lavy nothing male velke without pocitat it They zalozit everything they robit brought forth Tvoj Lord bol never unjust towards ktokolvek